<topic id='element_care_professional_main_specialty_code.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: CARE PROFESSIONAL MAIN SPECIALTY CODE - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>an3</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_care_professional_main_specialty_code">CARE PROFESSIONAL MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_main_specialty_code">MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_care_professional_main_specialty_code">CARE PROFESSIONAL MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 is the specialty in which the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_consultant">CONSULTANT</xref>
 is contracted or recognised. 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_main_specialty">MAIN SPECIALTY</xref>
 classifies clinical work divisions more precisely for a limited number of specialties.  </p>
  <p>
All 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 is identified by a pseudo 
    <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_care_professional_main_specialty_code">CARE PROFESSIONAL MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 of:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
560 - 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 - Midwife        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
950 - 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 - Nursing        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
960 - 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_non-consultant_led_activity">Non-Consultant Led Activity</xref>
 - Allied Health Professional.        </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>The default codes 199 and 499 are only applicable for overseas providers.</p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_care_professional_main_specialty_code">CARE PROFESSIONAL MAIN SPECIALTY CODE</xref>
 is used by the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/secondary_uses_service.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Secondary_Uses_Service</xref>
 to derive the 
    <b>
         <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/healthcare_resource_group.asp"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Healthcare_Resource_Group</xref>
      </b>
  
    <b>4</b>
. Failure to correctly populate this data element is likely to result in an incorrect 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/web_site_content/supporting_definitions/healthcare_resource_group.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Healthcare_Resource_Group</xref>
, usually associated with lower levels of healthcare resource.  </p>
  <p>
For further information, please refer to the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
    <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/secondary-uses-service-sus/payment-by-results-guidance"
            scope="external"
            format="html">Payment by Results Guidance</xref>
.  </p>


